Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:44.75,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕らは今日を生きて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.84,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}たとえどんな風が吹いても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:54.02,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何度でも自由を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:59.00,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}羽ばたいて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:03.36,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}悲しみも乗り越えた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:08.38,op_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.61,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将聚散离合深埋心间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:59.49,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前进的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:06.63,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}记忆总以柔和的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:11.17,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}对我们报以微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:15.25,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:18.41,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}与涛声一同作响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:24.69,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:29.37,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}让我们找到最初的勇气
