Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.92,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们张开心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:44.75,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度过一天又一天的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.84,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论面对怎样的风向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:54.02,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终朝着自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:59.00,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:03.36,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为那悲伤的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:08.38,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在着绽放的光芒
